      "content": "i tried the saline spray but it didnt really do anything and my head still feels like it's going to explode. i've read online that some doctors say it's actually fine in the second trimester if you only take a small dose. if i just take one pill instead of two, is that really going to be a big deal? i just need to be able to breathe so i can function.",
